long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Google Chrome extension that displays total monthly GitHub commits in your contributions graph.

Just install the extension, then go to yours or someone else's GitHub profile page to view the monthly total commits.
